						<summary>

						<p>Stone pillar in front of the Chennakēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>1798 A.D.</p>						

						<p>It is dated in Śaka 1720, Kālayukti, Nija-śrāvaṇa, śu. 15, corresponding to 1798, A.D. August 26, Sunday.</p>						

						<p>Records the set up of lamp stad <hi rend="italic">(dīpastaṁbam)</hi> by Pedagurvireḍi, the son of Vīrareḍi and the grand son of Nala Gurvi reḍḍi at Pāyasaṁpalle. He is said to the devotee of Vīrabhadra swāmi.</p>						

						</summary>
